\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\emph on
Matrix-matrix multiplication/product
\emph default
 (
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{R}^{m\times p}\times\mathbb{R}^{p\times n}\rightarrow\mathbb{R}^{m\times n}$
\end_inset

): 
\begin_inset Formula $C=A\,B\Rightarrow c_{ij}=\sum_{k=1}^{p}a_{ik}b_{kj}$
\end_inset

 (denoted by 
\begin_inset Formula $A*B$
