\emph on
linearly independent
\emph default
, then the 
\begin_inset Formula $a_{j}$
\end_inset

 are the 
\emph on
basis
\emph default
 of 
\begin_inset Formula $S=\mbox{span}\{a_{1},\dots,a_{n}\}$
\end_inset

